# Project Context

PasalasFijas API is the backend for a freemium football prediction platform powered by AI.

Stack:
- NestJS with TypeScript.
- Prisma ORM.
- PostgreSQL.
- pnpm.
- OpenAI prepared as the AI provider.
- DDD anemic entities.
- Lightweight hexagonal architecture.

Product model:
- Free users can view 2 complete predictions per day.
- Premium users can view all complete predictions.
- Locked predictions may be previewed by the frontend, but the backend must enforce access.
- The app is not a bookmaker and does not process real-money bets.

Core business domains:
- auth
- users
- plans
- subscriptions
- football
- predictions
- ai-analysis
- bankroll
- admin

Core business concepts:
- Match
- Team
- AiAnalysis
- Pick
- ComboBet
- Confidence
- RiskScore
- ValueScore
- NO_BET
- UserPredictionView
- Bankroll

Main business rule:
Never force a pick. If data is missing, risk is high, odds have no value, or signals contradict each other, return or force NO_BET.

Never expose raw secrets, provider tokens, or sensitive internals in API responses.
